metadata.name: Dizicord Access Key 2022
metadata.description: Dizicord is an exclusive NFT group. The key gives access to the Discord server. Our goal is to build a community of like-minded individuals interested in becoming better traders and building connections. With 100+ roles to pick from, you will only get notified about information that you care about. Traders of all skill levels are welcome. The beginner-friendly guides and organized server make information easily accessible to both novice and expert learners. There is an economy system that rewards users (with alpha bounties) for being helpful to one another. Rewards include ETH/NFT prizes and allowlist access to upcoming projects. Other benefits include project analyses, free tools/resources, and much more.
